<p>
The short diagonals of the faces of the <a href=3D"https://mathworld.wolfra=
m.com/RhombicTriacontahedron.html">rhombic
triacontahedron</a> give the edges of a dodecahedron (Steinhaus 1999, pp.&n=
bsp;209-210).
</p>
